---

<div class="flex flex-row justify-center align-middle mx-10 space-x-10">
  <div class="type dark:type-invert pt-16 leading-tight">
    <h1 class="text-xl font-normal">
      Hi there &#128075; <br />I'm <span class="text-2xl text-orange font-bold"
        >David
      </span>
    </h1>
    <h5 class="font-normal">
      I'm an aspiring software engineer. Devoted to building efficient,
      maintainable solutions.
    </h5>
    <div class="flex-row">
      <button
        class="bg-blue-dark dark:bg-yellow-bright text-light-txt dark:text-dark font-body font-bold py-3 mt-3 rounded w-1/3 hover:scale-110 hover:translate-y-1 ease-in-out duration-500"
        >Contact me
      </button>
      <button
        class="bg-yellow-dull dark:bg-lavender text-dark font-body font-bold py-3 mt-3 ml-4 rounded w-1/3 hover:scale-110 hover:translate-y-1 ease-in-out duration-500"
        >Contact me
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-h-[450px] max-w-[450px]">
    <img
      src="/heroImage.png"
      class="h-full w-full"
      alt="Hero Image. A picture of me looking off into the distance pensively."
    />
  </div>
</div>
